node.title: Latest: Prime Minister to hold urgent unscheduled press conference
node.content: ["The Prime Minister is holding an unscheduled and urgent Omicron press conference this morning.\u00a0", "Jacinda Ardern and Director General of Health Dr Ashley Bloomfield will speak with media at 11am.\u00a0", "It comes after several border-related Omicron cases in the past days including an airline, airport and MIQ worker.\u00a0", "This week Ardern said if Omicron moves beyond the border the whole country would move to red within 24-48 hours.\u00a0", "\u00a0", "What you need to know:", "App users click here for the latest updates"]
